#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Blocking calls"
msgstr "Bloqueio de chamadas"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`quarkus-smallrye-jwt` extension uses link:https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-jwt[SmallRye JWT] library which is currently not reactive."
msgstr "A extensão `quarkus-smallrye-jwt` utiliza a biblioteca link:https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-jwt[SmallRye JWT] , que atualmente não é reativa."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What it means from the perspective of `quarkus-smallrye-jwt`, which operates as part of the reactive Quarkus security architecture, is that an IO thread entering the link:https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-jwt[SmallRye JWT] verification or decryption code might block in one of the following cases:"
msgstr "Do ponto de vista `do quarkus-smallrye-jwt` , que opera como parte da arquitetura de segurança reativa do Quarkus, isso significa que uma thread de E/S que entre no código de verificação ou descriptografia link:https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-jwt[do JWT do SmallRye] pode ficar bloqueada em um dos seguintes casos:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The default key resolver refreshes the `JsonWebKey` set containing the keys, which involves a remote call to the OIDC endpoint."
msgstr "O resolvedor de chaves padrão atualiza o conjunto `JsonWebKey` que contém as chaves, o que envolve uma chamada remota ao endpoint OIDC."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The custom key resolver, such as `AWS Application Load Balancer` (`ALB`) key resolver, resolves the keys against the AWS ALB key endpoint by using the current token's key identifier header value."
msgstr "O resolvedor de chaves personalizado, como o resolvedor de chaves `do AWS Application Load Balancer` ( `ALB` ), resolve as chaves no endpoint de chaves do AWS ALB utilizando o valor do cabeçalho “identificador de chave” do token atual."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In such cases, if connections are slow—for instance, taking more than 3 seconds to respond to the key endpoint—the current event loop thread is likely to become blocked."
msgstr "Nesses casos, se as conexões forem lentas — por exemplo, se demorarem mais de 3 segundos para responder ao endpoint principal —, é provável que a thread atual do ciclo de eventos fique bloqueada."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To prevent it from blocking, set `quarkus.smallrye-jwt.blocking-authentication=true`."
msgstr "Para evitar que o sistema fique travado, defina `quarkus.smallrye-jwt.blocking-authentication=true` ."

